        <span class="docSource"><span class="dType"><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ draft ]">Dft</abbr></span> (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>).</span>
       </p>

      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA10d157n1-ptr" id="PJA10d157n1">1</a>
       
   <p>For <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s meeting with Adm. Lord Richard Howe on 11 Sept. 1776, see vol. <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0009" class="document">5:2021</a>; <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-02-02-0006-0010-0001&amp;expandNote=DJA02d292n1#DJA02d292n1" class="document">2:250</a>; <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0185%20ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0186%20ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0187#ADMS-01-03-02-pb-0417" class="pageNo">3:417431</a>; and <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Adams Family Correspondence&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1963. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Adams Family Correspondence</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-04-02-02-0080" class="document">2:124125</a>. The committees report was presented to Congress on 17 Sept. (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington C. Ford and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 17741789&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 19041937; 34 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 5:767768). The canceled passage may indicate that <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> considered quoting from the reports final paragraph containing the committees conclusions.</p>

